data.description: Wonderful home in the heart of Elk City.  3 Bedrooms 2 Full baths.  Beautiful flooring throughout the main living areas.  Nice kitchen with stainless appliances.  Large Master Bedroom and Bathroom has double sinks.  Wood burning fireplaces in the den with built in book shelves.  Backyard has a storm shelter, covered patio and workshop.  Call today to schedule a viewing.
